A basic HTML template for a web page announcing the web developer internship opportunities at Cognifyz Technologies:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Web Developer Internship Opportunities at Cognifyz Technologies</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Web Developer Internship Opportunities at Cognifyz Technologies</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="introduction">
            <h2>Join Our Team!</h2>
            <p>Cognifyz Technologies is excited to announce internship opportunities for aspiring web developers. If you are passionate about technology and eager to learn, this is the perfect opportunity for you!</p>
        </section>
        <section class="details">
            <h2>Internship Details</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Position: Web Developer Intern</li>
                <li>Location: Remote</li>
                <li>Duration: 3-6 months</li>
                <li>Start Date: Flexible</li>
                <li>Stipend: Competitive</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="requirements">
            <h2>Requirements</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Basic understanding of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript</li>
                <li>Strong problem-solving skills</li>
                <li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team</li>
                <li>Eagerness to learn and grow</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="apply">
            <h2>How to Apply</h2>
            <p>To apply for this internship, please send your resume and a cover letter to <a href="mailto:careers@cognifyz.com">careers@cognifyz.com</a>. We look forward to hearing from you!</p>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Cognifyz Technologies. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
CSS (styles.css)
/* Basic Styles */
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
}

header, footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1em 0;
}

header h1 {
    margin: 0;
}

main {
    padding: 2em;
}

section {
    margin-bottom: 2em;
}

h2 {
    color: #444;
}

ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: 1em;
}

a {
    color: #0066cc;
    text-decoration: none;
}

a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}
To create a contact information section in HTML.
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Information</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Contact Us</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="contact-info">
            <h2>Our Contact Information</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us using the information below:</p>
            <div class="contact-details">
                <p><strong>Address:</strong></p>
                <p>1234 Main Street</p>
                <p>Anytown, AN 12345</p>
                <br>
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong></p>
                <p>(123) 456-7890</p>
                <br>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong></p>
                <p><a href="mailto:info@cognifyz.com">info@cognifyz.com</a></p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Cognifyz Technologies. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
CSS (styles.css)
/* Basic Styles */
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
}

header, footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1em 0;
}

header h1 {
    margin: 0;
}

main {
    padding: 2em;
}

.contact-info {
    background-color: #fff;
    padding: 2em;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: left;
}

.contact-details p {
    margin: 0.5em 0;
}

a {
    color: #0066cc;
    text-decoration: none;
}

a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

